data.description: This is your chance to LEVEL up! Beautiful CRESTVIEW LAKES has the neighborhood setting that you are looking for WITHOUT the CDD! This is an executive-style GATED community with tree-lined streets, sidewalks, paver-driveways AND an 80 acre lake for kayaking or paddle boarding! WELCOME to your CLEAN, BRIGHT home LEVELED up with the better FEATURES that make a difference! This NORTHEAST facing spacious 2555 SF floor plan is a 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with XTRAS: 1st floor FLEX/BONUS room, 1st floor bedroom with full bathroom & a 17’x16’ 2nd floor LOFT!  The QUALITY interior offers SMART home bundling, VOLUME ceilings, NEUTRAL colors, 17”x17” diagonal tile patterned flooring & GRANITE countertops throughout (even the bathrooms)! The KITCHEN is surrounded with white 42” STAGGERED raised panel cabinets with CROWN molding and brushed nickel hardware + PULL OUT shelving in the lower cabinets + FULL hexagon mosaic tile backsplash + a closet pantry! ALL of the STAINLESS appliances are included: microwave, side by side fridge, range & newer Samsung dishwasher. The kitchen island breakfast bar is the focal point of this kitchen integrating dining and gathering!  Step OUTDOORS from the family room slider onto the 29’x9’ COVERED patio. The sunny backyard is a FULLY FENCED, DEEP yard with a 6’ vinyl privacy fence; total lot is 53’x130’.  The primary bedroom + 2 oversized bedrooms are on the 2nd floor! MORE INCLUDED features are: ceiling fans, water softener, kitchen sink water filtration, hurricane shutters, pre-wired security system, garage floor sealant, wifi boosters, hybrid water heater, LED lighting, washer/dryer and a money SAVING radiant barrier. Elementary school: less than a MILE! Middle and High School: less than 2 miles! GREAT location to travel into TAMPA or MACDILL AFB. SUPER location for access to dining, shops & grocery off of US 301! Under an hour to get to ST PETE BEACH! Floor plan and 3D tour is available!
